## 1C. Community composition

### Dissimilarity matrices

```{r
comm_mat <- as.matrix(comm[, species_cols])

# Presence–absence
comm_pa <- (comm_mat > 0) * 1
beta_jac <- vegdist(comm_pa, method = "jaccard")

# Abundance-based
beta_bray <- vegdist(comm_mat, method = "bray")
```

### NMDS ordination

```{r
set.seed(123)
nmds_jac <- metaMDS(comm_pa, distance = "jaccard", k = 2, trymax = 100)
nmds_bray <- metaMDS(comm_mat, distance = "bray", k = 2, trymax = 100)
```

